WEBVTT

00:00:01.313 --> 00:00:05.359 line:90% position:50% align:center
Each year, Jehovah’s Witnesses
hold conventions around the world

00:00:05.359 --> 00:00:07.361 line:90% position:50% align:center
in hundreds of languages.

00:00:11.365 --> 00:00:13.993 line:90% position:50% align:center
Those in attendance learn how the Bible

00:00:13.993 --> 00:00:16.579 line:90% position:50% align:center
can benefit them in practical ways.

00:00:21.751 --> 00:00:25.296 line:90% position:50% align:center
Our three-day conventions include
Bible-based talks . . .

00:00:25.296 --> 00:00:28.883 line:90% position:50% align:center
What a joy it is going to be
when “death will be no more,”

00:00:28.883 --> 00:00:30.677 line:90% position:50% align:center
removed forever!

00:00:32.011 --> 00:00:33.721 line:90% position:50% align:center
. . . interviews,

00:00:36.641 --> 00:00:39.019 line:90% position:50% align:center
and dramatic reenactments.

00:00:44.608 --> 00:00:48.695 line:90% position:50% align:center
All sessions are open to the public,
and attendance is free.

00:00:48.695 --> 00:00:52.449 line:90% position:50% align:center
Come and see for yourself
why millions attend each year.

00:00:53.575 --> 00:00:56.370 line:90% position:50% align:center
To learn about the next convention
to be held near you,

00:00:56.370 --> 00:00:59.164 line:90% position:50% align:center
ask one of Jehovah’s Witnesses
for more information

00:00:59.164 --> 00:01:01.792 line:90% position:50% align:center
or visit jw.org.

00:01:01.792 --> 00:01:04.461 line:90% position:50% align:center
Click About Us, then Conventions.

